  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THIS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While Red was working on teleportation technology, there was a sudden explosion and he's thrown into a whole different world! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/bd82ada11775fd80bbad5de5bd16c544.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/bd82ada11775fd80bbad5de5bd16c544.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JOURNEY THROUGH BEAUTIFUL WORLDS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Red explore different beautiful worlds as they try to find his way back home. Play through a gorgeous level of eye-catching and tranquil handmade art. Battle with different monsters, collect coins and gems, find the hidden runes, and unlock the exit portal to go back to your world! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAY AS RED </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like a knight in shining armor, help Red fight with monsters and free the Protectors of the Forest. Collect and upgrade weapons, coins and gems, find your way to the exit portal to  back home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/fc2c22445f8a62b05d848e87d34af82b.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/fc2c22445f8a62b05d848e87d34af82b.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=1200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HANDMADE ART</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy beautiful hand-painted scenery as you progress through the game. With such lovely artwork, the game is fun to play, even with slow gameplay and minimal battle mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/3d162866db0c596dee0c1c2b9d7688ee.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/3d162866db0c596dee0c1c2b9d7688ee.avif?t=1749203747 width=1170 height=658 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/96cfc0e6ce3c6c6d74cf9a23afbe0b54.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/96cfc0e6ce3c6c6d74cf9a23afbe0b54.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/1c9bbb74340a763da40fe2b1cb8f328b.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/1c9bbb74340a763da40fe2b1cb8f328b.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REVEAL THE HIDDEN CHESTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect the magic runes from chests hidden around the level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/c7833ed9cd26b43827352ceb1ad7f455.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/c7833ed9cd26b43827352ceb1ad7f455.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACTIVATE THE PORTAL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all the runes to unlock the portal and go back home!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/3097b248f7dd852b5940a90d788c5864.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/3097b248f7dd852b5940a90d788c5864.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Copyright 2022 S&I Games</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Artwork</strong> by MoonTribe, Fallencake Studio, DucVu FX, Mimu Studio </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Background Music</strong>, Woodland Music Album, Track 1, by GWriterStudio</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Title Page Music,</strong> Riding Dragons from RPG Puzzle Game Music by  Red Iron Labs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Instructions Page Music</strong>, Freebie - Visiting a Foreign Town from RPG Puzzle Game Music by  Red Iron Labs </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bird Sounds</strong> from Fantasy Adventurer Pack (60+ Tracks) by WhelpSounds </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sound effects</strong> from Casual Game Sounds by Dustyroom</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Only Title page and Steam store graphics (including Red's character portrait) have been created using ChatGPT</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THIS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While Red was working on teleportation technology, there was a sudden explosion and he's thrown into a whole different world! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/bd82ada11775fd80bbad5de5bd16c544.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/bd82ada11775fd80bbad5de5bd16c544.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JOURNEY THROUGH BEAUTIFUL WORLDS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Red explore different beautiful worlds as they try to find his way back home. Play through a gorgeous level of eye-catching and tranquil handmade art. Battle with different monsters, collect coins and gems, find the hidden runes, and unlock the exit portal to go back to your world! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAY AS RED </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like a knight in shining armor, help Red fight with monsters and free the Protectors of the Forest. Collect and upgrade weapons, coins and gems, find your way to the exit portal to  back home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/fc2c22445f8a62b05d848e87d34af82b.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/fc2c22445f8a62b05d848e87d34af82b.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=1200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HANDMADE ART</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy beautiful hand-painted scenery as you progress through the game. With such lovely artwork, the game is fun to play, even with slow gameplay and minimal battle mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/3d162866db0c596dee0c1c2b9d7688ee.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/3d162866db0c596dee0c1c2b9d7688ee.avif?t=1749203747 width=1170 height=658 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/96cfc0e6ce3c6c6d74cf9a23afbe0b54.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/96cfc0e6ce3c6c6d74cf9a23afbe0b54.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/1c9bbb74340a763da40fe2b1cb8f328b.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/1c9bbb74340a763da40fe2b1cb8f328b.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REVEAL THE HIDDEN CHESTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect the magic runes from chests hidden around the level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/c7833ed9cd26b43827352ceb1ad7f455.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/c7833ed9cd26b43827352ceb1ad7f455.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACTIVATE THE PORTAL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all the runes to unlock the portal and go back home!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras/3097b248f7dd852b5940a90d788c5864.avif?t=1749203747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214570/extras_big/3097b248f7dd852b5940a90d788c5864.avif?t=1749203747 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Copyright 2022 S&I Games</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Artwork</strong> by MoonTribe, Fallencake Studio, DucVu FX, Mimu Studio </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Background Music</strong>, Woodland Music Album, Track 1, by GWriterStudio</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Title Page Music,</strong> Riding Dragons from RPG Puzzle Game Music by  Red Iron Labs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Instructions Page Music</strong>, Freebie - Visiting a Foreign Town from RPG Puzzle Game Music by  Red Iron Labs </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bird Sounds</strong> from Fantasy Adventurer Pack (60+ Tracks) by WhelpSounds </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sound effects</strong> from Casual Game Sounds by Dustyroom</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Only Title page and Steam store graphics (including Red's character portrait) have been created using ChatGPT</i></p>",
